

.. Housing:

Housing


What type of housing exists and how do people live in it?

.. contents::
   :local:
   :depth: 10





.. _au.data.B02_Average_household_size:

Average household size
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------





Selected Medians and Averages





Measure "Average household size"  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B02_Average_household_size'
      );






Average household size is only available for point lookups.

.. _au.data.B01_Count_psns_occ_priv_dwgs_F:

Count of Persons in occupied private dwellings (Females)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------





Selected Person Characteristics





Measure "Count of Persons in occupied private dwellings (Females)"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B01_Count_psns_occ_priv_dwgs_F'
      );





Measure "Count of Persons in occupied private dwellings (Females)" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),
          'au.data.B01_Count_psns_occ_priv_dwgs_F'
        );






Measure "Count of Persons in occupied private dwellings (Females)" percent of "Total (Females)" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B01_Count_psns_occ_priv_dwgs_F',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Count of Persons in occupied private dwellings (Females)" percent of "Total (Females)" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),
        'au.data.B01_Count_psns_occ_priv_dwgs_F',
        'denominator'
      );

.. _au.data.B03_Count_home_Census_Nt_0_14_yr:

Counted at home on Census Night Age 0-14 years
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------





Place of Usual Residence on Census Night





Measure "Counted at home on Census Night Age 0-14 years"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B03_Count_home_Census_Nt_0_14_yr'
      );





Measure "Counted at home on Census Night Age 0-14 years" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),
          'au.data.B03_Count_home_Census_Nt_0_14_yr'
        );






Measure "Counted at home on Census Night Age 0-14 years" percent of "Counted at home on Census Night Total" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B03_Count_home_Census_Nt_0_14_yr',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Counted at home on Census Night Age 0-14 years" percent of "Counted at home on Census Night Total" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(

      OBS_GetMeasure(

      );

      );

.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B36_Dweling_structur_NS_NofB_NS'
      );

        );

      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Dwelling Structure





Measure "Other dwelling Number of bedrooms None includes bedsitters"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B36_Other_dwelling_NofB_0_i_b'
      );





Measure "Other dwelling Number of bedrooms None includes bedsitters" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),
          'au.data.B36_Other_dwelling_NofB_0_i_b'
        );






Measure "Other dwelling Number of bedrooms None includes bedsitters" percent of "Other dwelling Total" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B36_Other_dwelling_NofB_0_i_b',
        'denominator'
      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Dwelling Structure





Measure "Total Number of bedrooms Six or more bedrooms"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B36_Total_NofB_6_or_m'
      );

        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),
          'au.data.B36_Total_NofB_6_or_m'
        );

        'denominator'
      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Tenure Type and Landlord Type





Measure "Other tenure type Total"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B32_Oth_ten_type_Total'
      );





Measure "Other tenure type Total" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),
          'au.data.B32_Oth_ten_type_Total'
        );






Measure "Other tenure type Total" percent of "Total Total" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B32_Oth_ten_type_Total',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Other tenure type Total" percent of "Total Total" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),
        'au.data.B32_Oth_ten_type_Total',
        'denominator'
      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Tenure Type and Landlord Type





Measure "Owned outright Dwelling structure Flat unit or apartment"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B32_O_OR_DS_Flat_unit_apart'
      );





Measure "Owned outright Dwelling structure Flat unit or apartment" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),
          'au.data.B32_O_OR_DS_Flat_unit_apart'
        );






Measure "Owned outright Dwelling structure Flat unit or apartment" percent of "Owned outright Total" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B32_O_OR_DS_Flat_unit_apart',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Owned outright Dwelling structure Flat unit or apartment" percent of "Owned outright Total" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),
        'au.data.B32_O_OR_DS_Flat_unit_apart',
        'denominator'
      );

.. _au.data.B32_R_Tot_DS_Flat_unit_apart:

Rented Total Dwelling structure Flat unit or apartment
""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Tenure Type and Landlord Type





Measure "Rented Total Dwelling structure Flat unit or apartment"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B32_R_Tot_DS_Flat_unit_apart'
      );





Measure "Rented Total Dwelling structure Flat unit or apartment" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),
          'au.data.B32_R_Tot_DS_Flat_unit_apart'
        );






Measure "Rented Total Dwelling structure Flat unit or apartment" percent of "Rented Total Total" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B32_R_Tot_DS_Flat_unit_apart',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Rented Total Dwelling structure Flat unit or apartment" percent of "Rented Total Total" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),
        'au.data.B32_R_Tot_DS_Flat_unit_apart',
        'denominator'
      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Tenure Type and Landlord Type





Measure "Tenure type not stated Dwelling structure not stated"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B32_Ten_type_NS_DS_not_stated'
      );





Measure "Tenure type not stated Dwelling structure not stated" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),
          'au.data.B32_Ten_type_NS_DS_not_stated'
        );






Measure "Tenure type not stated Dwelling structure not stated" percent of "Tenure type not stated Total" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),
        'au.data.B32_Ten_type_NS_DS_not_stated',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Tenure type not stated Dwelling structure not stated" percent of "Tenure type not stated Total" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),
        'au.data.B32_Ten_type_NS_DS_not_stated',
        'denominator'
      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Tenure Type and Landlord Type





Measure "Total Dwelling structure Semi detached row or terrace house townhouse etc"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131),

      );

          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(-33.8806, 151.2131), 0.01),

        );
